By: \'Aziz ibn Muhammad al-Nasafi
---
The Universe is the mirror of God -- the mirror in which His majesty and
perfection are reflected, the mirror in which He sees Himself -- and the heart
of man is the mirror of the Universe; if the Traveler then would know God,
he must look into his own heart.
